WEBVTT

00:08:28.353 --> 00:08:30.988
mikono yangu ilikua na
baridi na yeye ana joto,

00:08:31.012 --> 00:08:34.424
nilichukua mikono yangu ya barafu
na kuisukuma ndani ya shati lake ...

00:08:34.886 --> 00:08:36.895
kuikandamiza kwenye mwili wake mkali.

00:08:36.919 --> 00:08:38.982
(Kicheko)

00:08:39.405 --> 00:08:41.920
Na alikua hapendi kabisa,

00:08:41.944 --> 00:08:42.965
(Kicheko)

00:08:42.989 --> 00:08:44.347
lakini alinipenda,

00:08:44.371 --> 00:08:49.228
na alivyokufa,
nililala kitandani na Aaron

00:08:49.252 --> 00:08:51.656
na nikaweka mikono yangu chini yake

00:08:53.355 --> 00:08:55.845
na nikahisi joto lake.

00:08:58.374 --> 00:09:01.881
Na sikuweza hata kusema kama
mikono yangu ilikua na baridi,